DESCRIPTION:0800 – 0830\n\n\n\n\n------------\n                    From: 
       Aaron Gilkey\n                    Sent:       Tuesday\, February 10\
 , 2026 10:43 AM\n                    To: John Woodward\; Chris Marshall\n 
                    Subject:    Wildcat Chorale Performance dedicated to Fi
 rst Responders\n\nThe Episcopal elementary school has called and invited u
 s\, along with other city agencies\, to attend their Spring Chaple Perform
 ance dedicate to first responders.\n\nThe Wildcat Chorale cordially invite
 s the first responders of our community to a special Spring Chapel perform
 ance dedicated to your service. We are deeply grateful for the dedication 
 and bravery you show every day in keeping us safe.\n\nPlease join us as Th
 e episcopal elementary school has called and invited us along with other c
 ity agencies to attend their Spring Chaple Performance dedicate to first r
 esponders.\n\nexpress our thanks through music.\n\n•       Date: Wednesd
 ay\, April 29\, 2026\n\n•       Time: 8:00 AM – 8:30 AM\n\n•       L
 ocation: Episcopal Collegiate Lower School Gym\n\nWhile we welcome all mem
 bers of your department to attend\, we would be honored to have at least o
 ne representative present to accept our thanks on behalf of your team.\n\n
 \nWhen\n\nWednesday Apr 29\, 2026 ⋅ 8am – 9am (Central Time - Chicago)
 \n\nLocation\n\nEpiscopal Collegiate School\, 1701 Cantrell Rd\, Little Ro
 ck\, AR 72201\, USA\nView map<https://www.google.com/maps/search/Episcopal
 +Collegiate+School\,+1701+Cantrell+Rd\,+Little+Rock\,+AR+72201\,+USA?hl=en
 >\n\n\n https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIh48oXm4D6v75iR8b683ZEZ0
 ydIYzxNd8KD5f-4kJgvI_wwk4=s288-c-no\n\nAaron Gilkey\nMedia & Relations Coo
 rdinator\nMetropolitan EMS\nT: 501.301.1425 | M: 501.400.4617\nE: aaron.gi
 lkey@metroems.org<mailto:aaron.gilkey@metroems.org>\n\nwww.metroems.org<ht
 tp://www.metroems.org/>\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/MetroEMSlraa https://t
 witter.com/MyCompany404 https://linkedin.com/company/mems-metropolitan-eme
 rgency-medical-services/ https://www.instagram.com/metroems/\n\n1121 W 7th
  St\, Little Rock\, AR 72201\n\n\nThe content of this email is confidentia
 l and intended for the recipient specified in message only. It is strictly
  forbidden to share any part of this message with any third party\, withou
 t a written consent of the sender. If you received this message by mistake
 \, please reply to this message and follow with its deletion\, so that we 
 can ensure such a mistake does not occur in the future.\n\n\n\n\n
